function registerCourse(){if(!preventRegister){var n=$("#courseId").val(),t=$("#courseTitle").text();$("#RegisterCourseId").val(n);$("#registerCourseTitle").text("ثبت نام "+t);$("#registercourse").slideDown(1e3,function(){window.location="#registercourse"})}}function showDetails(n,t,i,r){var u=$("#description_"+r).val();$("#courseTitle").text(t);$("#courseDescription").html(u);$("#coursePrice").text(i+" ريال");$("#courseId").val(r);$("#coursesdetails").slideDown(1e3,function(){window.location="#coursesdetails"})}function backToCourses(){window.location="#courses";$("#registercourse").hide();$("#coursesdetails").slideUp(1e3,function(){})}var preventRegister=!1;$("#RegisterForm").submit(function(n){n.preventDefault();var t={FirstName:$("#FirstName").val(),LastName:$("#LastName").val(),PhoneNumber:$("#PhoneNumber").val(),RegisterDescription:$("#RegisterDescription").val(),RegisterCourseId:$("#RegisterCourseId").val()};$.ajax({url:"/home/Register",dataType:"json",data:t}).done(function(){$("#registercourse").hide();$("#coursesdetails").hide();$("#successRegister").show();preventRegister=!0})});